title: 228: Central Nervous System FIRE!
description: The Central Nervous System or CNS is critical not only to your strength and performance, but to your ability to maximize muscle growth. How do you fire up your CNS? Sal, Adam & Justin tell you what to do. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpradio.com
